OL,3,CThree children in hospital after
OL,4,Csuspected norovirus outbreak at school
OL,6,FThree children have been taken to
OL,7,Fhospital after an outbreak of
OL,8,Fsuspected norovirus at a school near
OL,9,FWinchester.
OL,11,FHampshire County Council said that
OL,12,Fseven children in a class of 22 at
OL,13,FCompton All Saints Church of England
OL,14,FPrimary School reported having the
OL,15,Fvirus on Thursday (22 May), with three
OL,16,Fbeing hospitalised.
OL,18,FThe school is currently closed while a
OL,19,Fdeep clean takes place.
