OL,6,FCompton All Saints Church of England
OL,7,FPrimary School said: "The school is
OL,8,Fworking with UKHSA (UK Health Security
OL,9,FAgency) in managing cases of gastro-
OL,10,Fintestinal illness in students who
OL,11,Fattend our setting."
OL,13,FGirija Dabke, Consultant for Health
OL,14,FProtection at UKHSA South East, said:
OL,15,F"Viral gastroenteritis is an
OL,16,Fincredibly common cause of sickness
OL,17,Foutbreaks in community settings,
OL,18,Fincluding schools and nurseries,
OL,19,Fespecially during the autumn and
OL,20,Fwinter months.
