OL,6,F"Norovirus remains the commonest cause
OL,7,Fbut there are other viruses that can
OL,8,Fcause diarrhoea and vomiting (D&V) in
OL,9,Fyoung children, such as rotavirus.
OL,11,F"Symptoms of viral gastroenteritis
OL,12,Finclude nausea, vomiting and diarrhoea
OL,13,Fbut can also include a high
OL,14,Ftemperature, abdominal pain and aching
OL,15,Flimbs.
