OL,6,F"D&V can cause dehydration, especially
OL,7,Fin vulnerable groups such as young
OL,8,Fchildren and older or
OL,9,Fimmunocompromised people, so if you do
OL,10,Fget ill it is important to drink
OL,11,Fplenty of fluids during that time.
OL,13,F"If you have D&V, take steps to avoid
OL,14,Fpassing the infection on. Do not
OL,15,Freturn to work, school or nursery
OL,16,Funtil 48 hours after your symptoms
OL,17,Fhave stopped and don't prepare food
OL,18,Ffor others in that time either.
