OL,3,CThree children in hospital after
OL,4,Csuspected norovirus outbreak at school
OL,6,F"If you are unwell, avoid visiting
OL,7,Fpeople in hospitals and care homes to
OL,8,Fprevent passing on the infection in
OL,9,Fthese settings.
OL,11,F"Washing your hands with soap and warm
OL,12,Fwater and using bleach-based products
OL,13,Fto clean surfaces will also help stop
OL,14,Finfections from spreading. Alcohol
OL,15,Fgels do not kill norovirus so don't
OL,16,Frely on these alone."
